N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 899.81 - Selection of fiscal year

State Regulations
A cable television company may select any 12-month period
as its fiscal year for purposes of this Part. No cable television company may
change such fiscal year without having first obtained the written permission of
the commission. Notes
